{"tid":2033146,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗到個推廣同標準化廣東話既方法","createTime":"2020-05-24T12:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T23:25:10.000Z","uid":69696,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5121c77fc2d2a1f16d3dd3d5a95586fce6808f47","tid":2033146,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:57:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">就係整個全部用廣東話寫新聞既媒體</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內文全部用翻廣東話特有同正確既字，例如哋、嗰、啲等等，同埋用廣東話既俚語同中英夾雜<br />\n再加插專欄，講翻我地平時識講唔識寫既字／詞語，希望大家重新認識之餘，仲會陸續寫翻呢啲字出來<br />\n<br />\n我仲有個提議：<br />\n好多人唔打廣東話既字係因為速成入面，啲字排到好後；如果可以將呢啲排翻係前，取代少用既字，會唔會令更多人打翻呢啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"adb6d5a1f0ca0047aff81d45153d41cc19ca69f4","tid":2033146,"uid":159916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"有point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a876cc9cddb5ff2d85a2e32ad19dfc5e057c89f4","tid":2033146,"uid":140738,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"搞好廣東話拼音先有用<br />\n<br />\n就算張依啲字入哂新聞<br />\n<br />\n啲人望到唔識讀都係無意思<br />\n<br />\n況且書面語都係廣東話一部份"},{"pid":"23bde35d2a66ce95d6da1ff517f400819665e327","tid":2033146,"uid":69696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a876cc9cddb5ff2d85a2e32ad19dfc5e057c89f4","tid":2033146,"uid":140738,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"搞好廣東話拼音先有用<br />\n<br />\n就算張依啲字入哂新聞<br />\n<br />\n啲人望到唔識讀都係無意思<br />\n<br />\n況且書面語都係廣東話一部份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"我其實係針對本地人wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解香港會連一個廣東話媒體都冇？"},{"pid":"69129c2a8facbfda4ba946464d1fe0eb9e59ce69","tid":2033146,"uid":158411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s